<div class="container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to ILibrary, your ultimate destination for exploring and managing your reading journey. Our mission is to connect readers with books they love and to provide a seamless experience in discovering new literature.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>At ILibrary, we believe that reading enriches lives. Our goal is to foster a love for reading by providing a user-friendly platform where everyone can easily find, manage, and share their favorite books.</p>

    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2024, ILibrary began as a passion project to bring together book lovers. We started with a small collection and have grown into a vibrant community of readers and authors.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>Our dedicated team is composed of avid readers, software developers, and industry experts who are passionate about books and technology. Together, we work tirelessly to improve our platform and provide the best service to our users.</p>

    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>We invite you to explore our platform, join our community, and embark on your next reading adventure. Whether you are looking for new releases, classic literature, or insights about your favorite authors, ILibrary is here for you!</p>
